<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text">Natural disturbance processes probably do not involve fire to any great degree in most California stands, except for the cismontane ones. It can be top-killed by fire but is fire resistant because of moist, nonvolatile leaves and prolific sprouting. Fire may be more important currently for the alliance because of the invasion of annual, non-native grasses.</div>
	<table class="zebraStripe">
		
		<tr>
